<StratBox title="Should I Start Ozempic (or Mounjaro)?">
  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
    <li>✔ BMI ≥30, or ≥27 with metabolic issues</li>
    <li>✔ Fatty liver (NAFLD)</li>
    <li>✔ Prediabetes or insulin resistance</li>
    <li>✔ Hypertension paired with central obesity</li>
    <li>✔ Repeated failed weight-loss attempts</li>
    <li>✔ Strong appetite / food noise / emotional eating</li>
    <li>✔ Ready for weekly injections + long-term plan</li>
    <li>✖ Avoid if you have active pancreatitis or severe reflux</li>
    <li>✖ Avoid if pregnant or planning pregnancy within 6 months</li>
  </ul>
</StratBox>
